OL,3,CKing sends birthday card to Britain's
OL,4,Coldest man who turned 110 on Christmas
OL,5,CEve
OL,7,FBritain's oldest man has received a
OL,8,Fcard from Buckingham Palace to mark
OL,9,Fhis 110th birthday.
OL,11,FThe King sent a birthday card to
OL,12,FSecond World War veteran Donald Rose,
OL,13,Fwho marked the milestone on Christmas
OL,14,FEve.
OL,16,FDonald was born in 1914 and served on
OL,17,Fthe front line with the 7th Armoured
OL,18,FDivision.
