OL,3,CKing sends birthday card to Britain's
OL,4,Coldest man who turned 110 on Christmas
OL,5,CEve
OL,7,FHe joined the Queen's Royal Regiment
OL,8,Faged 25, and served in North Africa
OL,9,Fand Europe before training as a
OL,10,Fsniper. He survived a bullet to the
OL,11,Fleg.
OL,13,FTo mark his birthday, the Canal Vue
OL,14,Fcare home in Ilkeston in Derbyshire
OL,15,Fheld a wartime-themed party.
OL,17,FResidents and guests were treated to
OL,18,Fdancing and singing by Katie Ashby
OL,19,Ffrom Britain's Got Talent performers
OL,20,F"The D-Day Darlings", with Donald even
OL,21,Fjoining in with the dancing.
