OL,3,CKing sends birthday card to Britain's
OL,4,Coldest man who turned 110 on Christmas
OL,5,CEve
OL,7,F"A true national treasure"
OL,9,FCouncillor Kate Fennelly, the Mayor of
OL,10,FErewash, was among those at the party.
OL,11,FShe served in the RAF and described
OL,12,FDonald as "amazing and wonderful".
OL,14,FShe said "Donald is a lovely character
OL,15,F` and a true national treasure. The
OL,16,Fborough is proud to cherish him as its
OL,17,Fmost senior resident."
OL,19,FDonald's birthday cake was in the
OL,20,Fshape of a tank.
