OL,5,CEve
OL,7,FHe jokingly puts his longevity down to
OL,8,Fsalty water he had to drink during his
OL,9,Ftime as a Desert Rat.
OL,11,FDonald also stood to give a rendition
OL,12,Fof a poignant song he wrote to mark
OL,13,Fthe end of the war.
OL,15,FDonald's carer Naomi Allsop, says
OL,16,Fshe's hoping the lyrics he wrote can
OL,17,Fbe turned into a single.
